item.title: CVE-2020-15744|2024-08-04T13:22:30.724Z -- victure -- pc420
item.description: Stack-based Buffer Overflow vulnerability in the ONVIF server component of Victure PC420 smart camera allows an attacker to execute remote code on the target device. This issue affects: Victure PC420 firmware version 1.2.2 and prior versions.
